decoy pen
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a pen beside a dip or loading race where decoy stock are kept to encourage others.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
